    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman is the definition of 'mint.' Finished in a deep, glossy Jet Black Metallic that has been treated with a multi-stage paint correction and a premium ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless with zero chips, scratches, or swirl marks. The 19-inch Boxster S wheels are pristine, free of any curb rash, and wrapped in brand-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Inside, the black leather interior remains taut and supple, still retaining that factory-fresh scent; the bolsters show no wear, and the carpets have been protected by weather-mats since day one. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized Porsche dealerships with a full binder of records included. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service, brake fluid flush, and a multi-point inspection that returned a perfect bill of health. Always garaged under a soft cover and never driven in inclement weather, this Cayman offers a rare opportunity to own a modern classic in 'out-of-the-box' condition. Includes two keys, the original window sticker, and all owner's manuals.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in superlative condition, reflecting a level of preservation rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every aesthetic and mechanical detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for excellence. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a singular opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of engineering in its finest form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
