    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering crisp throttle response via six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS timing. The chassis is exceptionally taut, benefiting from documented subframe reinforcement and a factory limited-slip differential with a 3.62 final drive ratio. Mechanically flawless, it has undergone recent valve clearance adjustments and rod bearing prophylaxis to ensure peak internal health. Finished in pristine Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this M3 retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity and linear power delivery, offering an uncompromising analog driving experience for the discerning purist.",
